https://news.microsoft.com/en-xm/2020/07/16/how-global-disruption-can-have-local-implications/

Jumia is a beast. Working with giants to create a new giant. Guys please check out the chart. Green in a sea of red. 

$AMZN of Africa teamed up with $MSFT to mitigate disruption and help small and medium enterprises’ (SMEs) establish new supply chain avenues within Africa.

Digital platforms (like $JMIA) and adoption of mobile technology act as effective conduits for value exchange, by aggregating demand across the continent, these platforms give SME’s opportunities to access new markets, and to offer or identify goods/services previously limited by location constraints and marketing costs. These platforms create a diversification effect that boosts the robustness of supply chains. 

A powerful force expediting cross-border trade is the accelerating progress of digital technology in areas spanning from trade logistics, automated processing and e-payments to immediate access and exchange of trade information and documentation.
